</p>
<p>Losing a loved one is an incredibly painful experience, leaving a void that words can hardly fill.  Condolence messages, however, serve a vital purpose. They offer a lifeline of support, a tangible expression of sympathy in a time of profound grief.  They acknowledge the loss and remind the bereaved that they are not alone in their sorrow.</p>
    

